  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \n  \nThe root cause of this issue is similar to https://crbug.com/chromium/1400037, race condition UAF.  \n  \nioctl$DRM_IOCTL_MODE_CREATE_DUMB will call \\*drm_mode_create_dumb_ioctl\\* to crate \\*drm_gem_object\\*. If the gpu driver is evdi, it will finally call \\*evdi_dumb_c"
}